  "name": "Morrison COU1 — FDA generic centrifugal pump hemolysis credibility assessment (NC-1 clean)",
  "description": "V&V 40 credibility assessment for CFD hemolysis prediction of the FDA generic centrifugal blood pump under ventricular assist device (VAD) conditions. COU1 evaluates whether the computational model can predict relative hemolysis trends for a Class III VAD device at Model Risk Level 5. All 13 credibility factors are fully assessed with achieved levels meeting or exceeding required levels. Monte Carlo uncertainty quantification is performed across all operating points. Decision: Accepted.",
  "bindsRequirement": "https://uofa.net/synth/req/morrison-cou1-hemolysis-prediction",
  "bindsClaim": "https://uofa.net/synth/claim/morrison-cou1-cfd-hemolysis-adequate",
