      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "The CFD solver (OpenFOAM v9) is governed under a documented software quality plan including version control (Git, tagged releases), regression test suite (482 unit and integration tests, 100% pass rate), issue tracking, and change-control procedures. Code coverage of hemolysis-relevant modules exceeds 92%. An independent SQA audit was completed in Q3 2025 with no critical findings.",
