      "rationale": "Quantitative output comparison performed using validation metric E_rms for velocity fields and relative error for NIH. Statistical comparison accounts for both experimental measurement uncertainty (propagated via GUM) and numerical uncertainty (GCI-based). At all five operating points, the validation comparison metric U_val satisfies E < U_val, confirming the model is not invalidated. Graphical comparisons (scatter plots, Bland-Altman) supplement the quantitative metrics.",
      "acceptanceCriteria": {
