        "type": "AcceptanceCriteria",
        "description": "Validation comparison metric E < U_val at all operating points; quantitative metric defined a priori; experimental and numerical uncertainties propagated per GUM and ASME V&V 20 respectively; Bland-Altman analysis shows no systematic bias."
