      "rationale": "Validation experiments were conducted on the identical FDA generic centrifugal pump geometry at flow rates and speeds spanning the COU operating envelope. Fluid used in validation (ovine whole blood, hematocrit 38±2%) is representative of the intended clinical use. The five COU operating points are bracketed by validation conditions. Geometric fidelity between test article and simulation domain confirmed by CMM measurement (maximum deviation 0.08 mm).",
