      "rationale": "The turbulence model (SST k-ω) and hemolysis model (power-law Giersiepen-Wurzinger) are justified through literature review and sensitivity analysis. SST k-ω selected over k-ε based on superior performance in rotating confined flows (documented model selection study). Power-law coefficients calibrated against FDA interlaboratory hemolysis dataset. Model form uncertainty estimated at ±12% on NIH via ensemble of three alternative hemolysis models; this uncertainty is incorporated into the UQ budget.",
