      "requiredLevel": 3,
      "achievedLevel": 4,
      "rationale": "All model inputs (geometry, boundary conditions, fluid properties, hemolysis model coefficients) are documented with sources and uncertainty bounds in the simulation data package. Fluid viscosity measured at test temperature (NIST-traceable rheometer); density from literature with ±0.5% uncertainty. Boundary condition values derived from NIST-calibrated experimental measurements. Input uncertainty propagated through Monte Carlo analysis (N=4096). No inputs assigned without documented basis.",
